","msg":"<blockquote>有d話麻麻, 有d話好正, 都唔知睇唔睇好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得果10集<br />\n一星期睇哂啦"},{"pid":"0037528606bb7110d94ef975935fcfc44720b2db","tid":435352,"uid":60341,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T03:25:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d話麻麻, 有d話好正, 都唔知睇唔睇好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好當做一般懸疑偵探片睇<br />\n樓上有人同true detective, Sherlock 之類比我唔係咁同意<br />\nMH主線唔係查案，慢慢揭開變態殺手嘅心理建立現代犯罪心理學嘅過程先係主軸<br />\n反而查案只係證明理論有用嘅支線，有好多時啲case佢甚至冇畀到明確嘅結局<br />\n如果係想睇鬥智鬥力嘅疑犯追蹤，你揀錯戲睇"},{"pid":"03f10054cc6d29bf3cfd8b697f39350b87deed79","tid":435352,"uid":42202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:38:20.000Z","msg":"呢套好好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 肥谷應該當佢係真心朋友<br />\n肥谷感覺就係阿氏保加症既罪犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c38f0c424c7e2a93d2ad1589d483523f732b3d3","tid":435352,"uid":42202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現實中嘅FBI 30年前亂砌生豬肉草草結案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57349966&amp;category_guid=9999803&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57349966%26category_guid%3D9999803%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171019&d=gGjHpCzvCTPN%2BEj1HoMkczQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a212544d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57349966%26category_guid%3D9999803%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20171019&h=9669d462\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57349966&amp;category_guid=9999803&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20171019</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係sad既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class