tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第二季應該係主角比人停職，但係出左個無人搵到既連續殺人犯，跟住搵主角出山？</blockquote><br />\n可能好似Gotham咁<br />\n主角有段時間做左賞金獵人<br />\n無公職負擔可以用爛仔手段去輯兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c097ac87e94cacadf6d9dba98604a28da05404","tid":435352,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=5&amp;v=FDYBmNYc8IA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D5%26v%3DFDYBmNYc8IA&d=gGjHpCzvCTPN%2BEj1HoMkczQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=a98ad464\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=5&amp;v=FDYBmNYc8IA</a></blockquote><br />\n真谷德昭對答好似認真好多</blockquote><br />\n呢D犯如童年可以過得開心D<br />\n可能大個會做到個正常人<br />\n好多父母都會比好多壓力小朋友<br />\n人長期受壓好易失常"},{"pid":"97145f0c08aa0ff8efda4e8e7a3e8255cb19c6a4","tid":435352,"uid":7371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痴撚線david fincher<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後果集個肥佬睇到我成手都係汗<br />\n起晒雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時有下季!?!?</blockquote><br />\n我又未去到緊張到出汗<br />\n但最尾刻意營造到佢可以出手殺主角<br />\n最後原來只係一個抱抱<br />\n好大落差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者講主角同觀眾潛意識都會覺得對方可能再殺人<br />\n先入為主唔夠客觀<br />\n亦無左人與人之間基本嘅互信"},{"pid":"0371249ef9b8d9df2671c274d1b046f24aa3d53c","tid":435352,"uid":7371,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"成個S1我覺得節奏慢得滯<br />\n去到第6集先覺得較為開始黎料<br />\n如無耐性或唔多用腦嘅觀眾可能會睇幾集就棄劇<br />\n<br />\n但我喜歡佢探討連環殺人兇手嘅角度<br />\n想較為理性去做科學研究<br />\n盡早預防一個人慢慢去變成殺人兇手<br />\n但往往要接觸呢類犯需要大量人性去溝通<br />\n甚至要模仿對方嘅用語投其所好先可溝通到<br />\n<br />\nS1係啟發性大過娛樂性<br />\n但個結局算有娛樂性同有戲劇反高潮效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果繼續節奏咁慢<br />\n至少出三季都得<br />\n睇呢套劇感覺節奏似睇小說多過美劇<br />\n成日覺得主角遲早變痴線會殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071bf2acfeb1ff2423cb7e653d313c4cc5fe3c22","tid":435352,"uid":64865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:29:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇晒，最尾一集係正</blockquote><br />\n最尾 燒野果個係乜野人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係 kansas 另一個好出名既 serial killer<br />\nDennis Rader"},{"pid":"793ebcc7f4333da7d68959208acb3704e922c152","tid":435352,"uid":64865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T02:30:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想FINCHER拍返電影多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頂住當先 都好正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFincher 都係執導 1,2 + 9,10<br />\ntotal 4集"},{"pid":"0ad2435f216ac3953342fbfa5a9c15396832cd3e","tid":435352,"uid":87108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"fe630bb0af08645a72def81ceabe0c42ff6b4e5e","tid":435352,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"好想要個咁嘅阿頭<br />\n<br />\n識保住班靚又識幾時放手"},{"pid":"03d0eab62acf5cb8b1ccf4bf7de060d3d0db2dd9","tid":435352,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T07:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171101/1043349.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171101%2F1043349.htm&d=gGjHpCzvCTPN%2BEj1HoMkczQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=646539a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171101/1043349.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nMindhunter主角如果黎到2017年可能要訪問佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n8月尾先第一單 11月頭已經被人捉到 似乎佢都無做啲咩去逃避追捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b6d05c0035555d70b9d13c6d8a70792c195bb00","tid":435352,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T08:43:53.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e483dc4f1262fa17717fb96c723e41589962be3f","tid":435352,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T12:42:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171101/1043349.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171101%2F1043349.htm&d=gGjHpCzvCTPN%2BEj1HoMkczQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=646539a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171101/1043349.htm</a><br />\n<br />\nMindhunter主角如果黎到2017年可能要訪問佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n8月尾先第一單 11月頭已經被人捉到 似乎佢都無做啲咩去逃避追捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但可能佢已殺左好多個人<br />\n<br />\n係日本幾個月殺好多個人先比人知<br />\n其實佢都應該做左唔少野去掩飾"},{"pid":"2daf0c3c280ee2d03356d2e3d5861ded859a3ad1","tid":435352,"uid":12864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T21:01:13.000Z","msg":"追晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b41133c2f300a4864744286c7e91cc82d1d852","tid":435352,"uid":128904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T14:27:36.000Z","msg":"睇晒 好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nEd Kemper好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最尾Ed起身嗰吓我都嚇咗一嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91b53a6d90b38cfe78fca16e793f149ce12796f","tid":4